      • getDate

        public Date getDate()
        Returns the date the event happened. Keep in mind this might be and approximate date, and not all fields may actually be known. Also, it is recommended to get the formatted date string from getDateString() rather than just formatting the date this method returns.
        Returns:
        the date the event happened
        See Also:
        getDateString(), isAbout()
